The old man suddenly seems to disappear.
Then he speaks, and you can see him once more.
He says: Blending in is an old technique.  We all have done it at one
	 time or another.  However, Gaea helps us along, and helps us
	 disappear into the surroundings.  It's not perfect, and the less
	 experienced of us can only do it right half the time.  To make
         things even more disturbing, once we act, or do anything, except
	 look around, we are visible.  On one hand, it's a great ability,
	 but it is only useful in defense.
